channel.title: Sunny - Bob's Video Game OST: Mountain Boss [Soundtrack]
channel.description:
You might have seen @BobTheGUYYYYY video game collab thread around. It's nearing completion, and I expect to see Bob post up a playlist sometime in the next few weeks. Here's my latest contribution.
[![Sunny%20Presents%20Mountain%20Boss|500x500](upload://2joB8PA3Kr21hDkOEwaNEYTarca.jpeg)](https://soundcloud.com/alwayssunnyinlogan/bobs-video-game-ost-mountain) [[Click the pic or me!]](https://soundcloud.com/alwayssunnyinlogan/bobs-video-game-ost-mountain)
I prefer my [Ice Boss](https://soundcloud.com/alwayssunnyinlogan/bobs-video-game-ost-ice-boss) track for the collab more, but I enjoyed making a track that sounded HE-UGE.
